if PINCTRL_MSM

config PINCTRL_CANOE
	tristate "Qualcomm Technologies, Inc. CANOE pin controller driver"
	depends on GPIOLIB && OF
	help
	  This is the pinctrl, pinmux, pinconf and gpiolib driver for the
	  Qualcomm Technologies Inc Top Level Mode Multiplexer block (TLMM)
	  block found on the Qualcomm Technologies Inc CANOE platform.
	  Say Y here to compile statically, or M here to compile it as a
	  module. If unsure, say N.

